					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I've got (0x10000 * 2 + 0x4000 * 2) function pointers, one for each write/read for PPU/CPU. This makes the mapper code very simple (no "switch(address)") but most likely results in more cache misses for the cpu since those jump tables take about 650k of ram.</div>

